                    ## Direct download

                    Oskari packages are available on this site in `.zip` and `.tgz` formats.

                    Packages include:
                      * minified oskari build (`/min/oskari.min.js` and `min/oskari.min.css` files)
                      * language files (located under `/min`)
                      * sample `index.html` and `index.js` files
                      * sample `appsetup.json` and `config.json`
                      * stylesheets and image files

                    To get started, extract the package and open `index.html` in your web browser.
                    Note that the `appsetup.json` and `config.json` are fetched via ajax so you might need a web server to serve these.

